{"tid":1280163,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"部分保險不賠暴動損失 公帑埋單","createTime":"2019-07-03T01:24:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T02:22:00.000Z","uid":56881,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b6efaf4849e9d4cb2497e06f69492d3232020a3a","tid":1280163,"uid":56881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T01:24:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E4%BF%9D%E9%9A%AA%E4%B8%8D%E8%B3%A0%E6%9A%B4%E5%8B%95%E6%90%8D%E5%A4%B1-%E5%85%AC%E5%B8%91%E5%9F%8B%E5%96%AE-214500656.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E9%2583%25A8%25E5%2588%2586%25E4%25BF%259D%25E9%259A%25AA%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%25B3%25A0%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258B%2595%25E6%2590%258D%25E5%25A4%25B1-%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%25B8%2591%25E5%259F%258B%25E5%2596%25AE-214500656.html&d=ItsvLBlInL5d1alZeSWtsP7c%2B9HD3JYLAdxAiSxEDXo%3D&h=eda9b938\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E4%BF%9D%E9%9A%AA%E4%B8%8D%E8%B3%A0%E6%9A%B4%E5%8B%95%E6%90%8D%E5%A4%B1-%E5%85%AC%E5%B8%91%E5%9F%8B%E5%96%AE-214500656.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/sg7sY_IOABNDuiyxiRrMSQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-TW/thesun.hk.com/b93c82157662e48f092facdea3fc02ee\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fsg7sY_IOABNDuiyxiRrMSQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-TW%2Fthesun.hk.com%2Fb93c82157662e48f092facdea3fc02ee&h=980ea3fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n清潔工忙於在政總及立法會外清理。（何青霞攝）<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】立法會大樓於七一受到示威者衝擊，大樓的落地玻璃幕牆、鐵閘、圍欄等受到嚴重破壞，而大樓內的設施亦被損毀。保險界立法會議員陳健波表示，大樓結構本身是由政府負責，並沒購買保險，料維修費用將會由公帑支付，而立法會則有就大樓內的設施、系統設備及軟件購買保險全險，即使受到惡性破壞都有得賠償。<br />\n<br />\n陳健波昨接受訪問時表示，立法會大樓的結構包括玻璃幕牆、大門、鐵欄、電梯等均由政府負責，而政府物業向來都沒購買保險，故預料今次涉及大樓結構的維修費用將由公帑支付，費用可達數千萬元。<br />\n<br />\n陳健波：保險僅理賠千萬<br />\n<br />\n但對於大樓內的設施，如音響、廣播系統、保安系統等，立法會已購買高達一億元投保額的財產保險全險賠償，就算受惡性破壞亦可獲得賠償。陳健波又估計，如立法會大樓內的設施可獲賠償，金額或涉千萬元。<br />\n<br />\n立法會秘書長陳維安上月出席立法會內務委員會會議時，曾被問及有關立法會的保險問題。<br />\n<br />\n陳維安當時指出，立法會行政管理委員會有為立法會購買五類保險，當中僱員補償、財物全險和汽車保險在暴動情況下仍然會生效，但現金和公共責任保險在暴動下則無效。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔係暴動係咪可以claim保險"},{"pid":"9a04b54aba097c404e49ce40e31bf718c7e565fb","tid":1280163,"uid":49247,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T01:39:48.000Z","msg":"寵物展d參展商咪又係冇得claim，理由係天災<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"296a803edd2b984143f7d8e65d60fc6ad535e3b9","tid":1280163,"uid":22700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T02:12:34.000Z","msg":"政府都係用納稅人既錢 佢理尻得你"},{"pid":"b758e55adf9d0650a080d5810ea45d4850bc69ef","tid":1280163,"uid":26106,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T02:14:00.000Z","msg":"怕咩姐<br />\n人工島 港珠澳 高鐵都唔知用左幾多錢啦<br />\n港豬咪又係唔當一回事"},{"pid":"72305775bc27aa1318916bf0f68e130de406b5b1","tid":1280163,"uid":233815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T02:15:44.000Z","msg":"唔衝啲狗官邊有得賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"065c607bd339a8e0a69fccbfc9b1905c721db14e","tid":1280163,"uid":11719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a04b54aba097c404e49ce40e31bf718c7e565fb","tid":1280163,"uid":49247,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T01:39:48.000Z","msg":"寵物展d參展商咪又係冇得claim，理由係天災<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T02:22:00.000Z","msg":"人為都可以變天災，正苦要保險賠或唔賠都實有方法"}]}